OL,5, A bookseller says she was "delighted"  
OL,6, when Sir Patrick Stewart made a        
OL,7, surprise appearance to sign copies of  
OL,8, his new book.                          
OL,10,FThe actor dropped into The Woodstock   
OL,11,FBookshop in Oxfordshire when he saw    
OL,12,Fcopies of his memoir in the window.    
OL,14,FSir Patrick posted a video on X of him 
OL,15,Fsurprising Merle Esson when he visited 
OL,16,Fthe bookshop earlier.                  
OL,18,FMs Esson told the BBC it was "very     
OL,19,Fgenerous and supportive" of the actor  
OL,20,Fto drop in.                            
